## Styling Guidelines
- Use Tailwind CSS utility classes
- Follow [globals.css](mdc:website/app/globals.css) and brand tokens in [tailwind.config.js](mdc:website/tailwind.config.js)
- Mobile-first responsive design; consistent spacing and typography

## API Integration
- Follow [newsletter API](mdc:website/app/api/newsletter/route.ts)
- Proper error handling, validation, HTTP status codes
- TypeScript interfaces for request/response shapes

